<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[السَّنُون]</span>: ما يستاك به <span class="c2">«٤»</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>... فَعِيل<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
